ATTRIBUTION

This project is based on the excellent work of:

1. Chatbot UI by Mckay Wrigley
   Repository: https://github.com/mckaywrigley/chatbot-ui
   License: MIT
   Original Copyright (c) 2024 Mckay Wrigley

2. Inspired by OpenChat UI by imoneoi
   Repository: https://github.com/imoneoi/openchat-ui
   
The following major enhancements have been added:
- AWS Bedrock integration with streaming support
- Knowledge Base RAG implementation
- Character-by-character streaming display
- React popup widget for integration
- Multi-provider support (OpenAI + Bedrock)
- Enhanced model support (Nova, Claude, Llama)

